subject: Traffic Accidents and Safety
Football (College)
Roads and Traffic
lead_paragraph: The former Auburn tight end Philip Lutzenkirchen, a fan favorite who played on the 2010 national championship team, died in a one-car crash in Georgia, the state police said.
